Package org.shanerx.tradeshop.enumys

Enum Commands

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Commands>
org.shanerx.tradeshop.enumys.Commands
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Commands>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum Commands
extends java.lang.Enum<Commands>
Enum holding all commands as well as aliases, required permissions, minimum and maximum arguments, and whether or not command must be run by a player
